      abnormalities in these three networks. Further profiling revealed that patients 
      in subtype 1 had younger age of onset and more symptom severity as well as 
      greater deficits in cognitive performance than patients in subtypeÂ 2. 
      CONCLUSIONS: Overall, we identified two MDD subtypes based on SCNs that differed 
      in their clinical and cognitive profile. Our results represent a proof-of-concept 
